he land: and Joseph’s brethren came, and bowed down themselves before him with their faces to the earth.","year":-1707},{"id":"recGjKndPZ7WaMUSu","ref":"Gen.42.7","text":"And Joseph saw his brethren, and he knew them, but made himself strange unto them, and spake roughly unto them; and he said unto them, Whence come ye? And they said, From the land of Canaan to buy food.","year":-1707},{"id":"rec4Fs0AFKkFTflFF","ref":"Gen.42.8","text":"And Joseph knew his brethren, but they knew not him.","year":-1707}]}
